//! ## Protokol
//!
//! BBB (Bulk-Only Bulk) transport:
//! 1. CBW (Command Block Wrapper) → Bulk-OUT endpoint
//! 2. Data Stage → Bulk-IN veya Bulk-OUT
//! 3. CSW (Command Status Wrapper) ← Bulk-IN endpoint
